                            <img src="https://pixabay.com/get/g305b7c4b2c6665ef33071049370e79aea63dcd9ec49fa3db9fa007c94f9d6138fe8ad01c9d5e7166592bb636a38ebbf45e46c93bcc681fcd0a8630f4e54b97fd_1280.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded-circle" alt="השף הראשי">
                        </div>
                        <div class="member-details">
                            <h4>השף דוד כהן</h4>
